<plot>The story takes inspiration from a real case (Bruneri/Canella, Italy 1926). A man is hospitalized in a neurological clinic. He suffers from amnesia. Mrs Ballerini, after had seen his picture on the newspaper, realizes he is her husband and brings him her home. Also Mrs Polacich recognizes him as her husband. More, at one point he is brought to the court as Mr. Lo Bianco accused to be a thief. But soon all his identities are found false for different reasons. He will remain alone with just a dog as a friend.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?339880</url></doc>
